-- Areva Board Meeting Set for Tomorrow May Be Postponed, La Tribune Reports
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-11-15T05:39:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/areva-board-meeting-set-for-tomorrow-may-be-postponed-la-tribune-reports.html
Areva SA’s board meeting scheduled
for tomorrow may be postponed until the start of next week to
allow further time for negotiations with candidates to
participate in the company’s planned capital increase, La
Tribune reported, citing unidentified people.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  